{"slug":"petroninja","id":"5fb935f365b222001ef52ff9","uuid":"130db178-2b1e-4de8-b0f9-dacd0a1a288b","title":"Petro Ninja","html":"<figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://res-4.cloudinary.com/hq8qobwgy/image/upload/q_auto/v1/ghost-blog-images/petroninja.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><h2 id=\"overview\">Overview</h2><p>Established in 2014 and headquartered in Calgary, Canada, Petro Ninja helps more than 10,000 energy professionals access oil and gas data in a powerful web based platform. Use Petro Ninja's powerful web tools to extract well information, forecast production and create reports. Harness Petro Ninja's collaboration functionality across business units and the entire organization. Synchronize vital operations data and make informed decisions faster. I worked mainly on the mobile app in more than 1 year.</p><ul><li>Website: <a href=\"https://petroninja.com/\">https://petroninja.com/</a></li><li>iOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/petro-ninja/id1208288818\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/petro-ninja/id1208288818</a></li><li>Android: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.petroninja&amp;hl=en_NZ\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.petroninja&amp;hl=en_NZ</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"role\">Role</h2><p>When joined, I forked the <a href=\"https://github.com/react-native-mapbox-gl/maps\">react-native-mapbox</a> to fix fix some native issues, also write the unit tests. After that I helped enhancing the mobile app with more beautiful charts for oil industry. </p><h2 id=\"outstanding-solutions-and-technologies\">Outstanding solutions and technologies</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.mapbox.com/\">Mapbox</a></li><li>Oil industry data</li><li>Beautiful charts</li></ul>","comment_id":"5fb935f365b222001ef52ff9","feature_image":"https://res-4.cloudinary.com/hq8qobwgy/image/upload/q_auto/v1/ghost-blog-images/petroninja.jpg","featured":false,"visibility":"public","send_email_when_published":false,"created_at":"202